          <div class="post-author-info">
            <span class="post-author-name"><a href="profile.html">Luis Garcia Rangel</a></span>
            <span class="post-meta"><a href="post.html">March 5, 2026 at 11:30 PM</a></span>
            <span class="post-community"><a href="community.html">Computer Science Club</a></span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="post-body">
          <p>Just finished my submission for the spring hackathon — super glad that's done. Built a course scheduler that uses a constraint-satisfaction algorithm to avoid time conflicts.</p>
          <p>Ended up being way more complex than I expected once I added support for professor preferences and room capacity limits.</p>
          <p>If anyone wants to collaborate on cleaning it up and maybe open-sourcing it, let me know. Could be a solid portfolio piece for all of us.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      </div><!-- /.feed-column -->
    </main>

    <!-- Right Sidebar -->
    <aside class="right-sidebar">

      <div class="right-sidebar-section">
